   3.992551463826867*^9, 3.992551606056014*^9}, {3.9925518050802803`*^9, 
   3.9925518701474648`*^9}, {3.992551909683261*^9, 3.992551953298626*^9}, {
   3.992551992308588*^9, 3.992552024267477*^9}, {3.992552135243115*^9, 
   3.992552182694838*^9}, {3.992552247474331*^9, 3.992552252953891*^9}, {
   3.992556267271801*^9, 3.992556372058043*^9}, {3.992598653323943*^9, 
   3.992598654821154*^9}, 3.992599875353657*^9, {3.9925999329563236`*^9, 
   3.9925999809237175`*^9}, {3.9926000637487583`*^9, 
   3.9926001528440285`*^9}, {3.992600206367216*^9, 3.9926002582423477`*^9}, {
   3.992600290601425*^9, 
   3.9926003987670174`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"15a022d7-0b40-3b49-893c-\
a09f23d6601a"],

Cell["\<\
Henceforth, from these species examined, it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s known that in \
the natural world, prehensile tails are any tails used for grasping objects, \
stability, and locomotion.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992548803199799*^9, 3.9925488050973663`*^9}, 
   3.992549292314377*^9, {3.99254948992769*^9, 3.992549509391876*^9}, {
   3.9925495665773773`*^9, 3.992549619143268*^9}, {3.9925496722727623`*^9, 
   3.992549676444132*^9}, {3.99254971588214*^9, 3.992549733957552*^9}, {
   3.992549786484432*^9, 3.992549794880673*^9}, {3.992549827712153*^9, 
