9022a57b5fad"],

Cell["\<\
I then defined the torque exerted on the coordinate plane through generic \
placeholders. In this case, there is a point mass at (x,y) with mass m, \
distance r, and angle \[Theta] from the origin (0,0).\
\>", "Text",
