Cell["Given the above equation, the torque on this point would be:", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
  3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
  3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
  3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
  3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, {
  3.992601545006607*^9, 
  3.992601556366892*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d56db766-fb12-db4c-b555-\
bb43619adfdd"],

Cell["\[Tau] = m*g*r*sin(\[Theta])", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
  3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
  3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
  3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
  3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, {
  3.992601545006607*^9, 
  3.9926015577716312`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"46312698-4ec2-254a-a9a0-\
f3cd6a6f0ebb"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "However, there can be a right triangle drawn from the point mass to the \
origin with the x and y coordinates as legs and r as the hypotenuse as the \
above diagram shows. This means that the sine of \[Theta] would be ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   FractionBox["x", "r"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "26d6a054-48d8-fd4d-a066-8d6dd4d40b2b"],
 ". Plugging this into the above torque equation results in the following \
simplification:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
  3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
  3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
  3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
  3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, {
  3.992601545006607*^9, 
  3.9926015634098988`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fa939282-e97b-f14e-9ff2-\
085f83755ffd"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "\[Tau] = m*g*r*sin(\[Theta])\n\[Tau] = m*g*r*",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   FractionBox["x", "r"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a1ba5500-2d70-ec49-a3f9-d193428fa33a"],
 "\n\[Tau] = m*g*x"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
  3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
  3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
  3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
  3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, {
  3.992601545006607*^9, 
  3.992601561510029*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dd07b972-cc16-c747-93b0-\
14e8890e7ae9"],

Cell["\<\
Using the above simplification of the torque equation to build a helper \
function in Wolfram Language:\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992441396110668*^9, 
  3.992441416863719*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"279e8961-6d95-4ef4-872d-\
48c236b4d719"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"torqueAtPoint", "[", 
   RowBox[{"mass_", ",", "coord_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
  RowBox[{"mass", " ", "*", " ", 
   RowBox[{"coord", "[", 
    RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992098151403298*^9, 3.992098189069479*^9}, {
  3.992114260359228*^9, 3.9921142611536503`*^9}, {3.9926022136518803`*^9, 
  3.99260221921566*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3e46d2a0-8d26-455b-856c-\
604268fd7832"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "It\[CloseCurlyQuote]s also known that in order for the monkey to stay \
balanced when rotated to an angle of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6c8b08b8-d266-413e-901b-8ed3069a5e58"],
 " degrees, the sum of the torques has to equal zero. Recall that in the \
system, I had two point masses, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["m", "h"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "28d59367-e5eb-4939-95e5-c875e2e5b1ea"],
 " for the head and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["m", "t"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8244b1a1-38a7-4bbf-8a18-3af50bf3a956"],
 " for the tail. Their positions can be represented by the coordinates ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3336967b-1eec-49e9-aa90-861fab8c7614"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "4"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c252c901-f470-4631-9947-9c5a449cdd90"],
 ". It can also be expressed that the torque of the head is ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Tau]", "head"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "05e6e2ca-c24e-4066-86f9-85a592dc5ddc"],
 " and the torque of the tail is ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Tau]", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6835e406-04d8-4636-9aff-bbc8f9a8d7d5"],
 ". With this, I established that: ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Tau]", "head"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "14eaf9f0-2b25-449f-9d15-24ba25c4bb96"],
 " + ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Tau]", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4708b7ef-2729-41be-b208-28b8ec122ace"],
 " = 0 , or that the torques are equal and opposite:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
   3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
   3.992098145521916*^9}, {3.992098198772934*^9, 3.9920982084886703`*^9}, {
   3.9920982514498034`*^9, 3.992098335787692*^9}, {3.99209837208337*^9, 
   3.992098422464962*^9}, {3.992441427395996*^9, 3.99244142826186*^9}, {
   3.9925974785471573`*^9, 3.9925975064576387`*^9}, {3.99259869563301*^9, 
   3.9925987001896276`*^9}, 3.992601568413561*^9, {3.9926022987465973`*^9, 
   3.992602323794695*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"57155af2-8f58-4411-bd55-\
f593f752cbde"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Tau]", "head"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1146aa0d-730d-c54b-bdc9-1a4f99d0dbc6"],
 " = -",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Tau]", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f41dfdf8-8b75-dc47-b8e2-855fb68687a8"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
   3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
   3.992098145521916*^9}, {3.992098198772934*^9, 3.9920982084886703`*^9}, {
   3.9920982514498034`*^9, 3.992098335787692*^9}, {3.99209837208337*^9, 
   3.992098422464962*^9}, {3.992441427395996*^9, 3.99244142826186*^9}, {
   3.9925974785471573`*^9, 3.9925975064576387`*^9}, {3.99259869563301*^9, 
   3.9925987001896276`*^9}, 
   3.9926015694758167`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"5073f136-50fc-1545-9436-\
a4219ab10ffe"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "With that established, I created this simple model. It is important to \
recall that in the first set of variables, I did not define ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "cf5f5076-3fc6-ab4d-a3d4-34d85aa28612"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
  3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
  3.992098145521916*^9}, {3.992098198772934*^9, 3.9920982084886703`*^9}, {
  3.9920982514498034`*^9, 3.992098335787692*^9}, {3.99209837208337*^9, 
  3.992098422464962*^9}, {3.992441427395996*^9, 3.99244142826186*^9}, {
  3.9925974785471573`*^9, 3.9925975064576387`*^9}, {3.99259869563301*^9, 
  3.9925987001896276`*^9}, {3.9926023443927574`*^9, 
  3.992602355148279*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3974b004-8993-ec4c-8e7c-\
2e49ac523d9a"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "List of all known constants. Note that ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4646be59-45b8-40a2-9180-a91dff545d7a"],
 " is undefined:"
}], "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992441433444645*^9, 
  3.9924414505758963`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e5c343cc-3eee-4b31-bc83-\
94a759ea1680"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{
  "g", ",", "mHead", ",", "dHead", ",", "hHead", ",", "mTail", ",", "hTail", ",",
    "dTail"}], "}"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992098423964962*^9, 3.992098441919664*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[88]:=",ExpressionUUID->"1ad49a49-c482-4b91-b7ea-4a9d7096f08a"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{
  "9.81`", ",", "1", ",", "1", ",", "5", ",", "1", ",", "1", ",", "dTail"}], 
  "}"}]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.992098442293077*^9, 3.992098882142069*^9, 3.992114264860133*^9, {
   3.992115681232635*^9, 3.992115682460018*^9}, {3.992123343806863*^9, 
   3.9921233449405203`*^9}, {3.992124496197686*^9, 3.992124497232633*^9}, 
   3.992125989570477*^9, {3.992158998936428*^9, 3.992159022414731*^9}, {
   3.9921620064181623`*^9, 3.9921620423128242`*^9}, 3.992269607084392*^9, {
   3.992419903273837*^9, 3.9924199374808073`*^9}, 3.992425036556326*^9, {
   3.9924396793759327`*^9, 3.9924396810510893`*^9}, 3.9924427651408863`*^9, 
   3.992509667547757*^9, 3.992513098632375*^9, 3.99254539231043*^9, 
   3.9925455312730722`*^9, 3.9925456357821827`*^9, 3.992545756846517*^9, {
   3.9925471669844*^9, 3.992547183624094*^9}, 3.99254758380717*^9, 
   3.992554344369554*^9, 3.992591779575014*^9, 3.992592731489163*^9, 
   3.9925939008957863`*^9, 3.9925963129870453`*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[88]=",ExpressionUUID->"1a4118c5-6fa2-4f69-981f-7044157122ab"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "I did this because for the torques to stay in equilibrium in the model, \
when ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "15b0a43e-92d0-4e71-a0c7-604c0a00e89c"],
 " changes, one or more of the given variables also needs to change. If ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8ea85f49-fac4-4c65-be54-cda2d7e178f1"],
 " was a fixed length, but ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a0b8e3a3-79c1-4e26-96f0-7abf74a42488"],
 " changed, the system would not be in equilibrium. With this established, I  \
created a model that adjusts ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "25568895-182f-4c12-b6cb-75e8d3cefc8d"],
 " when ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "bbde8f61-5a38-4745-87f8-37db4a1eb6d9"],
 " changes."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.99209846209616*^9, 3.992098568364648*^9}, {
  3.9924414856306267`*^9, 3.992441487478155*^9}, {3.9925975084583597`*^9, 
  3.992597518503393*^9}, {3.9925987623918333`*^9, 
  3.99259877264497*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bc5468c4-3af2-4faa-92ce-\
b27aa7757ea3"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Wolfram\[CloseCurlyQuote]s built in NSolve function allows us to solve for ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "458d25f2-0e4a-4eba-85b2-f27f5cbc6392"],
 " using the model\[CloseCurlyQuote]s symbolic equations which include ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "56388a46-2b80-4f30-b9bd-c1bb799dfbd3"],
 ":"
}], "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992441492033078*^9, 3.992441512691023*^9}, {
  3.992598775996005*^9, 
  3.9925987762105227`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dcb8a83f-b8c7-41fb-b4c0-\
d0387f8a4118"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"NSolve", "[", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"torqueAtPoint", "[", 
     RowBox[{"mHead", ",", "p1"}], "]"}], "==", 
    RowBox[{"-", 
     RowBox[{"torqueAtPoint", "[", 
      RowBox[{"mTail", ",", "p4"}], "]"}]}]}], ",", "dTail"}], "]"}]], "Input",\

 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992098574045953*^9, 3.9920986100407753`*^9}, 
   3.992098849528429*^9, {3.9926084298870697`*^9, 
   3.992608432809826*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"47392bab-ad7f-4dab-8854-\
3294d8810b7f"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{"{", 
   RowBox[{"dTail", "\[Rule]", "5.215390309173472`"}], "}"}], "}"}]], "Output",\

 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9920986204777527`*^9, 3.992098624000496*^9}, 
   3.992098849786508*^9, 3.9920988822430677`*^9, {3.9920990136321363`*^9, 
   3.9920990165411777`*^9}, 3.9921142649384193`*^9, {3.992115681416601*^9, 
   3.992115682532655*^9}, {3.992123343882928*^9, 3.992123345019395*^9}, {
   3.9921244963204403`*^9, 3.992124497306608*^9}, 3.992125989665868*^9, {
   3.992158999075091*^9, 3.9921590225238*^9}, {3.992162007938998*^9, 
   3.992162042383925*^9}, 3.9922696071815*^9, {3.992419903383662*^9, 
   3.992419937544939*^9}, 3.992425036630001*^9, {3.99243967942551*^9, 
   3.992439681114352*^9}, 3.9924427652194777`*^9, 3.992509667676261*^9, 
   3.992513098688794*^9, 3.992545392422699*^9, 3.9925455313924627`*^9, 
   3.9925456358686867`*^9, 3.9925457569401407`*^9, {3.992547167099595*^9, 
   3.992547183713311*^9}, 3.992547584001133*^9, 3.992554347946958*^9, 
   3.9925917796801357`*^9, 3.9925927316033497`*^9, 3.992593901015345*^9, 
   3.992596313105771*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[89]=",ExpressionUUID->"37d21390-dfb5-452d-a5e6-aced45b84260"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The final part of this simple model is to form the real-time simulation. To \
do this, I programmed an input to change ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "42cbf8bc-a3d7-405c-bf8c-3d46adf90607"],
 ". This as a result changes the rotation of the monkey and the tail length \
of the monkey. The simulation\[CloseCurlyQuote]s code and output are \
visualized below, with UI allowing real-time adjustments to the leaning angle."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9920989413599586`*^9, 3.992098954672945*^9}, {
   3.992101728901793*^9, 3.9921017455229387`*^9}, {3.9921251093393593`*^9, 
   3.992125162972011*^9}, 3.992441619125505*^9, {3.992597522932423*^9, 
   3.992597549308612*^9}, {3.9926023894061623`*^9, 
   3.9926024110020695`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6eb4b0ef-83bd-40ba-959d-\
8cd8dbfb1097"],

Cell["\<\
Defining a function for all the prior computations listed above:\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992511895512957*^9, 
  3.9925119028171997`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"da75a920-edff-4381-bef3-\
b8b0eb153066"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"drawMonkey1", "[", "thetaLean_", "]"}], ":=", "\n", "\t", 
  RowBox[{"Module", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
     "p1", ",", "p2", ",", "p3", ",", "p4", ",", "p5", ",", "p6", ",", 
      "p5Visual", ",", "p4Visual", ",", "dTailValue"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
    "\t", "\n", "\t\t", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"p6", "=", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"0", ",", "0"}], "}"}]}], ";", "\n", "\t\t", 
     RowBox[{"p2", " ", "=", " ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
